        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes, the base prices are genuinely that low. The 'catch' is the same as any budget airline: the best prices are for earlier bookings and less popular times. If you book last minute for a Friday night, you'll pay more. But with some flexibility, you can access incredible deals that other bus companies simply don't offer.",
            "marks": []
