            "text": "FlixBus CL covers major cities like Santiago, Valparaíso, Concepción, and Temuco, as well as many popular tourist destinations. They are continuously expanding their network, so routes to places like the Atacama Desert or Puerto Montt are becoming more common. Check their website for the most current route map.",
